<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.196089>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 8. Adults of Scrobipalpa spp. 1, S. fusca sp. n. (HT); 2, S. latiuncella sp. n. (HT); 3, S. flavimaculata sp. n. (HT); 4, S. sattleri (Lvovsky & Piskunov) 5, S. divergens Povolný (HT); 6, S. erichiodes sp. n. (HT); 7, S. nigrigrisea sp. n. (PT); 8, S. distincta sp. n. (HT)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/196089/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.196091>
    dc:description "FIGURES 17 – 24. Male genitalia of Scrobipalpa spp. 17, S. fusca sp. n. (PT, slide no. 222 / 07); 18, S. latiuncella sp. n. (HT, slide no. 277 / 08); 19, S. flavimaculata sp. n. (HT, slide no. SYW 05309); 20, S. sattleri Lvovsky & Piskunov (slide no. SYW 05192); 21, S. divergens Povolný (HT, slide no. 210 / 07); 22, S. erichiodes sp. n. (PT, slide no. 101 / 08); 23, S. erichiodes sp. n. (PT, slide no. 74 / 08); 24, S. nigrigrisea sp. n. (HT, slide no. 88 / 08)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/196091/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.196094>
    dc:description "FIGURES 41 – 43. Female genitalia of Scrobipalpa spp. 41, S. fusca sp. n. (PT, slide no. L 06059); 42, S. sattleri Lvovsky & Piskunov (slide no. L 06063); 43, S. erichiodes sp. n. (HT, slide no. 75 / 08)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/196094/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

